{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783489433605,"sessionID":"ses_0bfd0dbd6ffenhLxBpSW8JdhPn","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_1794cd706d4047429300ca12","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Resource Map — glm52-5 Lineage\n\nEmitted from converged research-delta evidence (`config.resource_map.emit: true`). resource-map.md was NOT present at init (`config.resource_map_present: false`); this file is the post-synthesis coverage map, not a pre-existing exclusion set.\n\n## Coverage By Source Family\n\n| Family | Entries | Theme |\n|---|---:|---|\n| Commands | 3 | `deep_research_auto.yaml` spec.md-mutation branches + fan-out boundary; `/deep:*` command surfaces. |\n| Skills — runtime | 8 | `artifact-root.cjs`, `fallback-router.ts`, `fanout-pool.cjs`, `cli-guards.cjs`, convergence-floor test, lane-d packaging test, runtime package/tsconfig. |\n| Skills — workflows | 7 | `mode-registry.json`, reverse-coupling reducers/shims, `replay-graph-from-artifacts.cjs`, council test fixtures, deep-improvement named profile. |\n| Specs | 6 | Children 002/003/004 spec.md + plan.md; this phase's spec.md. |\n| Advisor | 4 | `skill_advisor.py`, `aliases.ts`, drift-guard, approved-divergences fixture. |\n| Model registry | 1 | `sk-prompt-models/assets/model_profiles.json` (GLM/MiMo quota pools + fallback_target). |\n| system-spec-kit | 2 | `mcp_server/package.json` test:council, `mcp_server/vitest.config.ts` include glob. |\n| Agents | 2 | `.opencode/agents` + `.claude/agents` deep agent mirrors. |\n| README | 1 | Root README deep-loop reference lines. |\n| Sibling graphs | 5 | system-spec-kit, system-skill-advisor, sk-code, sk-prompt, cli-opencode `graph-metadata.json` edges. |\n\n## Net-New Files Flagged As Gaps (relative to the Plan agents' design)\n\nThese are files the plan tables did not enumerate but the research found load-bearing:\n\n| File | Gap Class |\n|---|---|\n| `deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/deep-research-convergence-floor.vitest.ts` | REQ-002 enforcer; hardcodes old skill path |\n| `deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/meta-loop-lane-d-packaging.vitest.ts` | Asserts on named-profile filename |\n| `deep-loop-workflows/deep-ai-council/scripts/replay-graph-from-artifacts.cjs` | Third repair class (repo-root absolute probe) |\n| `deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/scripts/{reduce-state,runtime-capabilities}.cjs` | Class B omissions |\n| `deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/assets/non_dev_ai_system/profiles/deep-loop-runtime.json` | Ambiguous rename target |\n| `system-spec-kit/mcp_server/vitest.config.ts` | Silent test-set-shrink gate |\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-5/resource-map.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-5/resource-map.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-5/resource-map.md","time":{"start":1783489433597,"end":1783489433603}},"id":"prt_f40410ff9001lNP2K1cn3YaHR2","sessionID":"ses_0bfd0dbd6ffenhLxBpSW8JdhPn","messageID":"msg_f4040bf6c001P5uQxIq3mdhhzv"}}
