{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783489479430,"sessionID":"ses_0bfd0dbd6ffenhLxBpSW8JdhPn","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_b0b111d6fe994d728bb06416","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"{\n  \"openQuestions\": [],\n  \"resolvedQuestions\": [\n    \"Q1: Is folding deep-loop-runtime INTO deep-loop-workflows (as system-deep-loop) mechanically safe, and where does each component land?\",\n    \"Q2: How many bidirectional path-couplings exist between the two skills, and what breaks silently if a coupling is not repaired?\",\n    \"Q3: How does the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow (node_modules reach-ins + artifact-root re-export) behave post-merge, and is merging a net simplification or a net risk transfer?\",\n    \"Q4: What is the full reference-migration surface across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus/test literals/named profile files, and what is the risk of incomplete migration?\",\n    \"Q5: Should fallback-router.ts be wired for real GLM-5.2 -> MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback given it has zero callers today?\"\n  ],\n  \"keyFindings\": [\n    {\"id\":\"F-P0-001\",\"severity\":\"P0\",\"summary\":\"Detached fan-out lineage boundary conflicts with YAML spec.md mutation (not gated on fanout_lineage_artifact_dir).\",\"iteration\":1},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-001\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"Convergence-floor test (REQ-002 enforcer) hardcodes old skill name; Class A test-file count understated (7->10).\",\"iteration\":1},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-002\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"Class B reverse-coupling inventory incomplete: reduce-state/runtime-capabilities shims, orchestrate-session.cjs, continuity-thread require.\",\"iteration\":2},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-003\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"NEW third path-repair class: replay-graph-from-artifacts.cjs repo-root absolute existence-probe breaks silently.\",\"iteration\":2},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-004\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"Council test fixtures are semantic data, not path references; add to residual-grep allowlist.\",\"iteration\":2},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-005\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"test:council include glob can silently shrink the test set; needs non-empty-match assertion.\",\"iteration\":3},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-006\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"Divergence-ledger reason prose embeds old name; must update with structured fields.\",\"iteration\":3},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-007\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"Named benchmark profile deep-loop-runtime.json has ambiguous rename target.\",\"iteration\":3},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-008\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"classifyLineageFailure routes quota/auth to FATAL, making fallback wiring unreachable for GLM quota-out.\",\"iteration\":4},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-009\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"Registry id vs provider slug mismatch needs a normalizer before resolveFallback.\",\"iteration\":4},\n    {\"id\":\"F-P1-010\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"summary\":\"External-prose surface broad: 10 agent files + README + 5 sibling graphs needing edge-collapse.\",\"iteration\":5}\n  ],\n  \"ruledOutDirections\": [\n    \"runtime/ as a mode-registry entry (category error)\",\n    \"Per-replica spec.md writeback in fan-out (races on generated fence)\",\n    \"replay-graph as a Class B relative-hop site (repo-root absolute probe)\",\n    \"Global find/replace of deep-loop-runtime in council tests (semantic data)\",\n    \"Decoupling runtime TS tooling during merge (failure modes indistinguishable)\",\n    \"Dynamic mode-registry reads on advisor hot path (intentional coupling avoidance)\",\n    \"Naive single-call-site fallback wiring (unreachable for quota/auth)\",\n    \"Same-provider cross-pool fallback (graph validation rejects)\",\n    \"Renaming /deep:* commands or public agent names (public surfaces stable)\"\n  ]\n}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/